{"tid":1819850,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣大選】潛逃4年通緝犯  高雄投票時落網","createTime":"2020-01-11T07:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T08:58:13.000Z","uid":55198,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73f225ef242a3bd74e12196c95b9a40cf8745485","tid":1819850,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"2020-01-11 14:36 文字大小<br />\n高雄市莒光國民小學票站有通緝犯落網。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n台灣的總統及立法委員選舉今日舉行，全台各地投開票所湧現人潮，不過高雄市莒光國民小學票站，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今天上午有盜竊通緝犯現身投票。警方，待通緝犯一投完票，隨即上前攔查</span></span></strong>，並將犯嫌帶返四海派出所接受詢問。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報道，警方擒獲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">46歲姓龔盜竊通緝犯遭地檢署通緝長達4年之久</span></strong></span>，警方密切追蹤疑犯一段時間，掌握他最近出沒高雄市左營、楠梓一帶，今天在投開票所執勤警員發現龔的行蹤，按兵不動，直到龔<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投完票才上前攔查</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯措手不及，被拘捕時還直說，長年都在外地工作，並不知道被通緝。警方詢查後把疑犯解送橋頭地檢署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf49978525b615919523897df96b655239a27591","tid":1819850,"uid":241979,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"都要投埋票先拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5076cd554b00a4b590cf8c5b43c9efbef45e8198","tid":1819850,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"香港遲下唔投奶支派就係犯法即刻拉"},{"pid":"1281ba40d26c7fb53ae98d70715481f2f3439566","tid":1819850,"uid":315761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"竟然俾佢投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets